title: Optimize DataObject value conversion for TRUE/FALSE
type: issue
--- 
Currently DataObject uses a system like:

        case value
        when "TRUE"  then true
        when "FALSE" then false
        else dup ? value.dup : value
        end

This requires getting the symbol value then doing a string compare... totally wasteful.  There should be a way to identify the TRUE/FALSE symbols and return them immediately.